WEBVTT

00:00.148 --> 00:04.000
Petpuls gives a dog a voice that a human can understand.

00:04.274 --> 00:10.204
With this device, we humans can understand and communicate better,...

00:10.625 --> 00:12.731
...more accurately and more effectively.

00:13.960 --> 00:18.994
When a dog barks, the dog's barking sound will be collected through this device...

00:19.143 --> 00:23.109
...and then those voice files will be transferred to our main server...

00:23.673 --> 00:29.046
...and in this main server, our Petpuls unique voice recognition system and algorithm...

00:29.162 --> 00:35.432
...will analyze a dog's voice, and then in real time, it will be sent back to our application...

00:35.770 --> 00:38.207
...with a different emotional status.

